latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Finding homes in aamchi Mumbai is a task in itself. There’re certain requirements a house has to meet for it to be called as one’s dream home! 

On top of that, it’s always better to go with established players who know their market! Veterans like Provident housing, a Puravankara company @puravankara_official known for its quality of developments across 9 cities is now in Mumbai with their first residential project, Palm Vista near Shilphata Junction.

Palm Vista is a tropical themed residential project that offers apartments designed with multiple balconies, modern convertible furniture, lavish open spaces, and all the latest amenities.

You can also visit their super cool construction museum at sales office in Shilphata to take a sneak peek into their construction quality. 

I absolutely love how @ourprovidenthousing is setting the norm and providing the most value for money living spaces in entire Mumbai! If you’re intrigued like me as well, go check out Palm Vista!

Disclaimer: The space shown in the visuals is not Palm Vista and is not a representation of any of their properties, existing or future.

#PalmVista #ATropicalParadise #ProvidentInMumbai  #ProvidentHousing #Puravankara
